# mdplab

**mdplab** is an educational reinforcement learning laboratory designed to
accompany a textbook and teaching materials.

The library focuses on:
- Clear MDP abstractions
- Algorithmic transparency
- Compatibility with Gymnasium, PyTorch, and TorchRL

> This project is under active development.

